      • CONSTRUCTOR_UNDEFINED

        static final BaseFunction CONSTRUCTOR_UNDEFINED
        Undefined constructor, Reflect is special - there is like always constructor present, but sometimes it is not accessible by design... Let's say it's private or such, i.e. class is not designed to be instantiated. Normal native object will return null on baseConstruct, but reflected objects should return this constructor instance in this case, cause they are really not going to be created if no legit constructors are available.
